## Usage Examples

```
TDD: employee creation endpoint returns 201 with the created employee
RED: average salary by country includes only active employees
GREEN: AverageSalaryService.by_country returns Decimal aggregated mean
REFACTOR: extract EmployeeRepository from EmployeeService
AUDIT: app/services/insights.py
TESTS: app/api/routes/employees.py
SEC: app/db/queries.py
BUG: insights endpoint returns 500 when country has no employees
ULTRA ALT3: seeding strategy for 10k employees on SQLite
PRE: shipping the salary insights API without pagination
DELPHI: best approach for deterministic seed data
```
